{
  "stem": "16.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the three boys that my aunt had that were drafted in the army-- the youngest one heard what's going on, and so on.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he, he made his way home through one of those furlough papers that I printed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He wanted to say goodbye to his girlfriend.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was about three years older than I was, maybe, maybe four.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Germans caught him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they threw him in the-- in the boxcars.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They beat him up and threw him in the boxcars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He wound up in, in Auschwitz, also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In fact, he had the number-- my number is 4344.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "His number was 4345.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And his brother-in-law's number-- he had older sisters that were married-- his brother-in-law's number was 4343.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He was with me in the camp all throughout-- almost to the end.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The reason I say almost-- we got separated in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was to-- almost near the end.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he lives in Haifa, Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to visit him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was very happy to see me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, and this younger-- the younger son that came to say goodbye to his family, he never made it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After three weeks, we got separated in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know how many people there were, but we were packed in like herrings practically.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just-- it was just suffocating, hot, smelly.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- you had your bathroom right there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you didn't go out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't ever open the doors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if somebody was screaming that somebody had died or something, they still didn't open the doors.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it, it was just a horrible trip that I, I want to forget.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I can't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't want to forget.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I want to forget.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I think they gave you water.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
